{"tid":1994440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[技術性討論] 如果遊行集會個目的係教大家點預防武漢肺炎，咁會唔會違反限聚令？","createTime":"2020-04-29T12:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T13:41:25.000Z","uid":6883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c489589ba14776ab5ae3b6ed376ee96b5ea851a","tid":1994440,"uid":6883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"第599G章 《預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)規例》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599G!zh-Hant-HK?INDEX_CS=N\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap599G%21zh-Hant-HK%3FINDEX_CS%3DN&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=b3a96f36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599G!zh-Hant-HK?INDEX_CS=N</a><br />\n3.禁止在指明期間進行羣組聚集<br />\n(1)在指明期間內，不得在任何公眾地方進行羣組聚集。<br />\n(2)第(1)款不適用於 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)附表1所指明的<strong>豁免羣組</strong>聚集；及<br />\n(b)根據第5(1)條獲准許的羣組聚集。<br />\n<br />\n10.要求受禁羣組聚集解散等的權力<br />\n(1)在符合以下條件的情況下，獲授權人員可要求在公眾地方進行的聚集解散 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)該人員合理地相信，該聚集屬受禁羣組聚集<br />\n附表1 [第3條] 豁免羣組聚集<br />\n12.為<strong>傳揚有助於預防及控制指明疾病的資訊</strong>或技巧(或為處理有助於預防及控制指明疾病的供應品或物品)而進行的羣組聚集<br />\n<br />\n指明疾病 (specified disease)指2019冠狀病毒病，即本條例附表1第8A項所指明者； (2020年第52號法律公告)"},{"pid":"10d719ccb166eddb73bc7f6963e0308bc46c92c7","tid":1994440,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"如果啲狗試睇內文同按條文指引做嘢嘅話，係有機會嘅。<br />\n<br />\n不過而家連黃色嘅派口罩/消毒用品 都俾狗狗用限聚令搞， 你估下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba16de9ff865a57959fb58589db204af8c0da7a","tid":1994440,"uid":6883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10d719ccb166eddb73bc7f6963e0308bc46c92c7","tid":1994440,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"如果啲狗試睇內文同按條文指引做嘢嘅話，係有機會嘅。<br />\n<br />\n不過而家連黃色嘅派口罩/消毒用品 都俾狗狗用限聚令搞， 你估下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:41:25.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出po都係大家都可以試下用條文大下啲狗 <br />\n<br />\n不過追尾都係啲狗玩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}